    "Third, prompts specifically designed for ChatGPT do not universally apply to other commercial LLMs like Bard, as shown in Section III.",
    "Consequently, it is necessary to have a versatile and adaptable attack strategy, which could encapsulate semantic patterns while maintaining the flexibility for deployment across different LLM chatbots.Instead of manually summarizing the patterns from existing jailbreaks, we aim to leverage the power of LLMs to capture the key patterns and automatically generate successful jailbreak prompts.",
    "Our methodology is built on the text-style transfer task in Natural Language Processing.",
    "It employs an automated pipeline over a fine-tuned LLM.",
    "LLMs exhibit proficiency in performing NLP tasks effectively."
